title: Hour 1 - US Open, Kyrie Irving
itunes:title: Hour 1 - US Open, Kyrie Irving
description:
Dan and the Danettes discuss the biggest news from the weekend: Matt Fitzpatrick's win at the US Open, the continuing Deshaun Watson drama in the NFL and Kyrie Irving possibly joining a new team in the NBA.
